 class="row-start-1 col-start-1 relative z-[2] min-w-0"><div><div class="standard-markdown grid-cols-1 grid [&amp;_&gt;_*]:min-w-0 gap-3 standard-markdown"><p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Structure claire. Voilà ce que je lis :</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Le cœur fonctionnel — <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">src/</code></strong></p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Fichier</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Rôle</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">osmo_epdg_app.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Point d'entrée application</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">osmo_epdg_sup.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Superviseur (arbre de processus)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">epdg_ue_fsm.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Machine à états — session UE côté ePDG</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">aaa_ue_fsm.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Machine à états — authentification UE</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">gsup_server.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Lien vers OsmoHLR (port 4222)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">epdg_gtpc_s2b.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Interface GTP-C S2b vers PGW</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">epdg_diameter_swm.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Interface SWm (ePDG ↔ AAA)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">aaa_diameter_swx.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Interface SWx (AAA ↔ HSS)</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">aaa_diameter_s6b.erl</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Interface S6b (auth PGW)</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Les <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">.dia/</code></strong> — dictionnaires Diameter, pas du code Erlang, définitions de protocoles.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Le <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">TODO.md</code></strong> — poste son contenu, c'est important. Si des interfaces sont non implémentées, ça change tout le plan.</p>
