<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Différence factuelle pour une session VoWiFi :</strong></p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold"></th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">DB</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">gen_statem</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Vitesse</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">lecture/écriture disque</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">RAM pure</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Durée de vie</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">persistante</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">durée de la session</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Partage</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">plusieurs processus</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">un seul processus</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">Panne</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">survivra</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">perdu</td></tr></tbody></table></div>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Pourquoi gen_statem ici :</strong></p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]">Une
 session VoWiFi dure quelques minutes, n'a pas besoin de survivre à un 
reboot, et enchaîne des transitions très rapides (authentification, 
tunnels, signalisation). La DB serait un goulot d'étranglement.</p>
<hr class="border-border-200 border-t-0.5 my-3 mx-1.5">
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Conclusion factuelle :</strong> les deux approches sont valides. Le choix dépend du besoin. Ici : éphémère + rapide = RAM.</p></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="flex justify-start opacity-0 group-hover:opacity-100 group-focus-within:opacity-100 transition" role="group" aria-label="Message actions"><div class="text-text-300"><div class="text-text-300 flex items-stretch justify-between"><button type="button" data-cds="Button" class="cds-reset group/btn relative isolate inline-flex shrink-0 items-center justify-center gap-1.5 whitespace-nowrap select-none border-0 outline-none rounded h-control font-sans text-body font-medium [&amp;:disabled:not([aria-busy])]:opacity-50 disabled:pointer-events-none transition-shadow duration-fast focus-visible:shadow-focus text-primary aria-pressed:text-accent aspect-square w-control px-0  !text-muted hover:!text-primary" aria-label="Copier" data-testid="action-bar-copy"><span aria-hidden="true" class="absolute -z-[1] rounded-[inherit] transition-colors duration-fast group-focus-visible/btn:shadow-[inset_0_0_0_1px_var(--cds-page-bg)] bg-transparent group-hover/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover group-aria-expanded/btn:bg-fill-ghost-hover inset-0 group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent group-hover/btn:group-aria-pressed/btn:bg-accent cds-btn-squish "></span><span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1 "><span class="relative"><span data-cds="Icon" style="font-family: var(--font-anthropicons, Anthropicons-Variable); font-feature-settings: &quot;liga&quot; 0; font-optical-sizing: auto; font-style: normal; font-variation-settings: normal; line-height: 1; width: 1em; height: 1em; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0; user-select: none; font-size: 20px; font-weight: 433.3;" class="transition-all opacity-100 scale-100" aria-hidden="true"></span><span data-cds="Icon" style="font-family: var(--font-anthrop