<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><strong>Applications référencées dans sys.config :</strong></p>
<div class="overflow-x-auto w-full px-2 mb-6"><table class="min-w-full border-collapse text-sm leading-[1.7] whitespace-normal"><thead class="text-left"><tr><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Application</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Source dispo</th><th scope="col" class="text-text-100 border-b-0.5 border-border-300/60 py-2 pr-4 align-top font-bold">Remarque</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">osmo_epdg</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">✅</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">modules src complets</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">gtp_u_kmod</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">❌</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">dépendance externe — module kernel</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">gen_socket</code></td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">❌</td><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top">dépendance externe — lib C</td></tr><tr><td class="border-b-0.5 border-border-300/30 py-2 pr-4 align-top"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">lager</code></td><td class="border