>.</p>
<p class="font-claude-response-body break-words whitespace-normal leading-[1.7]"><code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sys.config</code> est chargé au démarrage, pas compilé dedans. Tu peux modifier <code class="bg-text-200/5 border border-0.5 border-border-300 text-danger-000 whitespace-pre-wrap rounded-[0.4rem] px-1 py-px text-[0.9rem]">sys.config</code> sans recompiler.</p>
